<h1>Contact Us</h1>

<p>Welcome to Luwa Store, where you can find various options to follow your hobbie on TGC. Whether you're looking for TCG pokemon or accessories to play, our platform connects you with the best options around. Feel free to get in touch if you have any questions, need assistance, or just want to say hello!</p>

<p>We would love to hear from you. If you have any inquiries, suggestions, or feedback, please fill out the contact form below and we'll get back to you as soon as possible.</p>

<div class="contact-form">
  <h3>Contact Form</h3>
  <%= form_with url: contact_path, method: :post, local: true do |form| %>
    <div class="form-group">
      <%= form.label :name, "Your Name" %>
      <%= form.text_field :name, class: "form-control", required: true %>
    </div>

    <div class="form-group">
      <%= form.label :email, "Your Email" %>
      <%= form.email_field :email, class: "form-control", required: true %>
    </div>

    <div class="form-group">
      <%= form.label :message, "Your Message" %>
      <%= form.text_area :message, class: "form-control", required: true, rows: 5 %>
    </div>

    <%= form.submit "Send Message", class: "btn btn-primary" %>
  <% end %>
</div>

